  "text": "Smk1-HH proteins were purified from meiotic cells under denaturing conditions as previously described (Corbi et al., 2014) . Briefly, 2 × 10 8 sporulating cells (8 h after transfer to sporulation medium) were collected by centrifugation. Collected cells were lysed with NaOH, and proteins were precipitated with trichloroacetic acid (TCA). Precipitated proteins were resuspended in denaturing buffer and purified with nickel beads [CITATION_1] .",
